data.description: This 4-bed, 3 Full Bath home with a roomy living area and a kitchen boasting plenty of cabinet and counter space. The master suite is on the main level, along with the 2nd bedroom, and upstairs, two more large bedrooms await. The full unfinished basement presents opportunities for added living space and is waiting for your personal touches.  Attached to the house is a 30x40 pole barn, ideal for a garage or workshop. Outside the home you’ll find 1 acre of property, a deck overlooking a tree lined back yard, and an additional 20x30 building. This property is ready for you to make it yours.
